imdb.plot outline: Every day, thousands of videos are uploaded to the internet. But is that incredible viral video you just viewed real? Using scientific analysis and digital forensics we'll discover who made the videos, how and why? You'll never watch a viral video the same way again!
imdb.title: Real, Fake or Unknown
